Stimuli placeholders
====================

The `.jpg` files in this directory are 1x1 black JPEG placeholders included
only to satisfy the BIDS validator's check that every `stim_file` referenced
in the events/behavioural TSVs resolves to a real file on disk.

The actual stimulus images are face photographs drawn from a restricted-access
database and cannot be redistributed with this dataset. To obtain the
originals, contact the dataset maintainer.

Filename convention: `SHINEd_<id>_<age>_<sex>_<emotion>_<version>.jpg`
  - emotion: `h` = happy, `a` = angry
  - version: `a` / `b` denote two exemplars per identity
